R K Swamy Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 21/05/2025 inter alia to consider and approve 1. The Audited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company for the quarter and financial year ended March 31 2025;

2. To consider and recommend Dividend if any on Equity Shares of the Company for the financial year 2024-25 and 

3. Any other business with the permission of the Chair.

Pursuant to Regulation 30 and 33 of the SEBI Listing Regulations we hereby notify that the Board of Directors of R K SWAMY Limited (the Company) at its Meeting held today i.e. February 12 2025 through video conferencing at the Registered Office of the Company which commenced at 10.00 AM (IST) and concluded at 1.20 P.M (IST) has inter alia considered and approved the following:

1. Un-Audited Consolidated Financial Results of the Company along with the Limited Review Report thereon for the quarter and nine months ended December 31 2024; (Enclosed as- Annexure- I);

2. The Un-Audited Standalone Financial Results of the Company along with the Limited Review Report thereon for the quarter and nine months ended December 31 2024 (Enclosed as - Annexure- II);
